    <description>This agent is designed to enable efficient collaboration between Relationship Managers and internal teams by acting as a centralised interface within Slack for research, communication, and workflow execution. It helps Relationship Managers submit and track research queries, retrieve relevant insights from internal knowledge sources, and connect with subject matter experts across research, product, and trading teams. In addition, the agent supports the initiation and tracking of approval workflows for custom trades or non-standard client requests. The overall goal is to streamline internal processes, reduce turnaround time, improve visibility into request status, and enhance the quality and speed of decision-making through intelligent, context-aware assistance.</description>
